---
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = "en;
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Yohann Zhao" description="About Yohann Zhao">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about myself and my background."
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="/assets/at-work.jpg"
					alt="个人工作照片"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> makes people happy. Sed
						do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Proin nibh nisl condimentum
						id venenatis a condimentum vitae. Dapibus ultrices in iaculis nunc. Arcu odio ut sem nulla
						pharetra diam sit amet. Diam quis enim lobortis scelerisque fermentum dui faucibus in ornare.
					</p>
					<p>
						Arcu dui vivamus arcu felis bibendum ut tristique et egestas. Eget gravida cum sociis
						natoque penatibus. Cras fermentum odio eu feugiat pretium nibh. Proin nibh nisl
						condimentum id venenatis. Porta nibh venenatis cras sed felis eget velit. Id diam vel
						quam elementum pulvinar etiam non.
					</p>
					<p>
					HI, I’m Yuhan Zhao, you can call me Yohann. I’m 24 years old.
					I majored in air transportation at Nanjing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics. I 
					studied airports and airlines. I have interships in Beijing capital international and Nanjing 
					Lukou international. During my college time, I was also the club leader of our university’s 
					flight-sim club. I participated in National university Flight Simulation championship, and 
					won the 2nd place. 
					After graduation, I came to Australia for an integrated training program. I finished the training 
					in 13months. Now I hold a CASA Commercial Pilot Licence with current Multi-Engine Class 
					Rating and Multi Engine Instrument Rating. I have 239 flying hours, mostly on the DA40NG 
					and DA42VI. I communicate in English and Mandarin. I have IELTS academic 8.0 and ICAO 
					AELP level 6 approved by CASA.
					So, my strengths are simple: I want to learn. I abide by SOPs. If don’t understand I always 
					ask, and I reflect on my performance after each flight. Instructors know me as disciplined 
					and well prepared.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>Corporis voluptates tenetur laudantium.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>officia unde omnis</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>
